name: mileposttenths
notes: Idaho State Highway System Tenth mile point locations. Generated by dynamic segmentation on road network centerline. This dataset contains for each Segment Code (ITD Road ID Code) the Begin Milepoint, End Milepoint and tenth mile incremented milepoints in between. Generated on ITD's Linear Referencing model
